{"timestamp": "2026-05-27 12:46:44,600", "level": "INFO", "logger": "flow.execution", "module": "flow", "function": "run_async", "line": 205, "message": " - task2: ```python\n[\n  \"1. Python Coding: Given a list of strings, write a function to group anagrams together. Discuss your algorithm’s time and space complexity, and how you would test it.\",\n  \"2. Microservices Design: Based on your experience at Acme Corp, describe the architecture of one of the microservices you designed, focusing on its key responsibilities, data storage, and communication patterns. How did you handle fault tolerance and scalability?\",\n  \"3. Docker & Kubernetes: At Acme Corp, you used Docker and Kubernetes. Can you provide a concrete example of how you optimized a Docker image for size and a Kubernetes deployment for performance or cost? What tools did you use to monitor performance?\",\n  \"4. AWS Architecture: You migrated a legacy application to AWS. Describe the specific AWS services you used (e.g., EC2, S3, RDS) and justify your choices based on scalability, cost, and performance requirements.\",\n  \"5. RESTful API Design: You built RESTful APIs in Python and Java at Acme Corp. Describe your approach to API versioning and ensuring backward compatibility. Provide an example of a versioning strategy you implemented.\",\n  \"6. Data Structures & Algorithms: Implement an LRU cache in Python. Explain how you would ensure thread-safety if it’s accessed concurrently in a high-traffic microservice.\",\n  \"7. Coding Exercise (Live): Write a function that reads a log file, counts the frequency of different error types, and returns the top 5 most frequent errors. Include edge-case handling and discuss performance considerations.\",\n  \"8. Database Optimization: At BetaTech Solutions, you optimized SQL queries. Describe a specific scenario where you improved query performance by 30%. What techniques did you use (e.g., indexing, query refactoring, schema changes)?\",\n  \"9. Behavioral Question: Tell me about a time you disagreed with a teammate on a technical design decision at Acme Corp. How did you handle the conflict, and what was the outcome?\",\n  \"10. Resume Deep Dive: Walk me through the most challenging project you worked on at Acme Corp. What were the key technical hurdles, and how did you overcome them using Docker, Kubernetes, and AWS services?\",\n  \"11. Candidate Questions: What questions do you have for me about the technical stack, team culture, or the specific challenges we are tackling in this role?\"\n]\n```"}
